'''Ma'Haffee Shipyard''', known coloquially as '''The Shipyard''' by locals, was an influential [[Starship/Legends|starship]] modification and repair company that was located in the [[Cularin system/Legends|Cularin system]]. It was owned by [[Trace Polters]].

The following starships were available in new condition at the Ma'Haffee Shipyard during the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]]:
*[[Barloz-class medium freighter/Legends|Barloz-class medium freighter]]
*[[Firespray-31-class patrol and attack craft/Legends|Firespray-31-class patrol and attack craft]]
*[[GR-75 medium transport/Legends|GR-75 medium transport]]
*[[Gun tug/Legends|Gun tug]]
*[[ILH-KK Citadel-class civilian cruiser]]
*[[S40K Phoenix Hawk-class light pinnace]]
*[[YT-1300 light freighter/Legends|YT-1300 light freighter]]
*[[Z-95 Headhunter/Legends|Z-95 Headhunter]]

